A compiler translste the compiler source program in a single line but Interpreter translate the source program line by line.
Compiler is faster and Interpreter is slower than compiler.
Compiler consumes less time and Interpreter consumes more time than compiler.
Compilers are large in size and Interpreters are smaller in size.
Compiler is used by programming language sucn as c, c++, java,c# etc. and Interpreter is used by programming languages such as Python, PHP, Perl, Ryby etc.